            <div class='post' itemprop='text'>
              <p>The current implementation of this feature is a bit confusing. What it does is if the query has a refresh schedule, it will refresh its widget in the dashboard based on this refresh schedule.</p>
<p>It seems that what most people expect it to do is to just refresh the queries regardless‚Ä¶ I‚Äôm planning to revise this feature and allow to refresh the widgets on the dashboard regardless of the query refresh schedule.</p>
            </div>

